overview: The unprofessional conduct continues when a suddenly unemployed Autum applies for a job at lesbian lover Jasmine's firm. But Autum soon learns that bitchy blonde boss Kate has a weakness for brunettes, and she'll stop at nothing to get doe-eyed Jasmine in her bed. Meanwhile, Kate's favorite "girl-toy" Taylor Vixen craves the touch of a girl her own age, and young, blonde coworker Lily is more than happy to oblige. Starring Autum Moon, Kate Kastle, Jasmine Jem, Taylor Vixen and Lily Labeau.
title: Lesbian Office Seductions 6
